name: David LUSICK, Petitioner v. Judge Jacqueline ALLEN, Judge John Herron and Judge Pamela Pryor Cohen Dembe, Respondents

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 14th day of December, 2012, the “Petitioner [sic] for Review -with Sanctions” is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the names of the jurists from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
